Package com.fdmgroup.PCTrack.model

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
com.fdmgroup.PCTrack.model.Staff
Direct Known Subclasses:
RoomAdmin
@Entity public class Staff extends Object
This object represents the role of a user in the company. It is the most basic role in the web application with the most basic permissions which are basically read only permissions. It is from this entity where the admin roles inherits in the following order (with increasing permission levels): Room, Location, Business. Note that a user can have multiple Staff objects in it.
